---
title: Premium Fillet Steak & Onion-Parsley Sauce with Parmesan Mash & Sautéed Greens
description: Make a flavour-packed sauce to drizzle over a tender cut of premium beef steak using onion, herbs and garlic. Then,
finish off your gourmet creation with creamy mash and vibrant greens.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/premium-fillet-steak-onion-chive-sauce-490572ee.jpg
